prodNameC: 羅氏可霸斯免疫分析骨鈣素檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagents - working solutions
M        Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 6.5 mL:
          Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL; preservative.
R1       Anti-N-MID Osteocalcin-Ab~biotin (gray cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL:
          Biotinylated monoclonal anti-N-MID Osteocalcin antibody (mouse)
          1.5 mg/L; phosphate buffer 100 mmol/L, pH 6.0; preservative.
R2       Anti-N-MID Osteocalcin-Ab~Ru(bpy)2+3 (black cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL:
          Monoclonal anti-N-MID Osteocalcin antibody (mouse)
          labeled with ruthenium complex 1.3 mg/L; phosphate buffer 
          100 mmol/L, pH 6.0; preservative.

CalSet - working solutions
• OSTEOC Cal1: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
• OSTEOC Cal2: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
Osteocalcin (synthetic peptide, human sequence) in two concentration ranges (approx. 0 ng/mL and approx. 280 ng/mL) in a human serum matrix.
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民權東路3段2號10樓
efficacy: 為體外定量檢測人類血清及血漿中N-MID骨鈣素的免疫分析法。N-MID骨鈣素的測定是用於監控骨質疏鬆或高鈣血症的病患(舉例)進行抗吸收治療時的治療效果。Electro-chemiluminescence immunoassay “ECLIA”是預定使用於 Elecsys和cobas e免疫分析儀上。Elecsys N-MID骨鈣素 CalSet是使用在Elecsys和cobas e免疫分析儀上，以供校正定量的Elecsys N-MID骨鈣素分析法之校正液組。
